{"tid":1570172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大部分香港人在政治上，是膽怯的，是無能的，是痴線的。","createTime":"2019-09-15T02:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T03:59:39.000Z","uid":41901,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e0653f1b6305a9fd70ea220ddafaecf644a201","tid":1570172,"uid":41901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"自己用腦參考一下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：鬥爭期間叫喊「香港人，加油...」？你是痴線的。大部分香港人在政治上，是膽怯的，是無能的，是痴線的。故此我講出下面的話，他們會說陳雲是癲佬：<br />\n革命鬥爭，第一件事就是<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>分清敵我</strong></span>，革命是exclusive的，排斥性的。你叫「香港人加油」，就是inclusive，包容性的，是維穩的。<br />\n「香港人，加油...」衙差也是香港人，他們也加油，拘捕之後跪斷你頸，入新屋嶺加油輪姦，整夜不停，大部分女義士入醫院被發現子宮出血而不敢作證，否則會被跳樓、被送入大陸活摘器官。<br />\n藍絲帶也是香港人，他們聽了「香港人，加油...」，就拿刀劈你，拿棍圍毆你。<br />\n「驅逐共黨，光復香港」，你不夠膽叫？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">孫中山當年就是叫「驅逐韃虜」，即使他的同盟會勢單力弱，孫中山的口號叫對了，最終成功推翻滿清。</span></strong><br />\n你也許叫過這個口號，會因為我這段話而憎恨我。真話不會入屋，入屋的是賊。我是請你出屋，重見天日，故此我的話不會入你的屋。"},{"pid":"781327841b884e801d8196be842703f25ff67bab","tid":1570172,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bbcf3a79ac5e8f7cf40968932f5e4d8366bb4c","tid":1570172,"uid":239842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"因為我地係講緊真。香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔通人地大陸講中國人加油又係講緊我地？"},{"pid":"c2ee23abf75077432a36deedf3092a277ddc3d79","tid":1570172,"uid":41901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0bbcf3a79ac5e8f7cf40968932f5e4d8366bb4c","tid":1570172,"uid":239842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"因為我地係講緊真。香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔通人地大陸講中國人加油又係講緊我地？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"又咁講 差佬同藍絲好多都係土生土長 一樣毫不留手"},{"pid":"17f8e236d7ddb16a0aeed6ba4e54f355f7a13eac","tid":1570172,"uid":24944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:57:49.000Z","msg":"係呀，去和理非周街唱the star-spangled banner就會贏㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n一時叫人韜光養悔和理非到美國法案通過<br />\n一時又話人出街唱歌拉人鏈係麻木不仁<br />\n<br />\n人哋去搵美國lobbying就話人賣港，要揸住紅旗打紅旗<br />\n到自己想痴去美國度又扮自己先係正途<br />\n<br />\n陳雲根，我睇咗你七年<br />\n每本著作都有買<br />\n<br />\n雨傘唔係輸勇唔勇武，和唔和理非<br />\n係輸滲透、輸內閧<br />\n你同你班信徒食屎啦！！！"},{"pid":"ceca3fdfc43e1b560785a42d99cab8b1f99fbb5e","tid":1570172,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"695cd2a63c481a75ac21b5c09f876ef18bd78b78","tid":1570172,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ee23abf75077432a36deedf3092a277ddc3d79","tid":1570172,"uid":41901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0bbcf3a79ac5e8f7cf40968932f5e4d8366bb4c","tid":1570172,"uid":239842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"因為我地係講緊真。香港人<br />\n<br />\n唔通人地大陸講中國人加油又係講緊我地？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"又咁講 差佬同藍絲好多都係土生土長 一樣毫不留手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"咁就算係咁。對運動結果根本毫無影響。<br />\n分分鍾光復香港時代革命 個引領性更強。<br />\n香唔香港人加油根本無咩討論空間，叫對了口號亦唔會贏，贏係贏戰略，唔係口號。"},{"pid":"d63a76e0f2fb08bad6330baa44ef00c1ca104c22","tid":1570172,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:02:06.000Z","msg":"香港人加係on9 但對和理非 淺黃比較有共鳴感"},{"pid":"43fdb14a4bb2585e614d1c52f8040e7e601f8722","tid":1570172,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"某程度啱，但陳雲自己無辦法宣傳開去，係邊個問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8bef9409b7d4462e4121516ceb1e5f88ffc896","tid":1570172,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"各有各叫啦<br />\n不分化<br />\n<br />\n起碼藍絲唔會叫香港人加油掛？"},{"pid":"433ddd7588bca4b313192526618a02ddba17e732","tid":1570172,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:21:56.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地開心啦，尋晚中秋前線小朋友食得一個包咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1797dca83dc591951948df9447aee733c390715b","tid":1570172,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4782e15de2cfae9cab23ab662615720da451ed","tid":1570172,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/152112_1520d0fcbdd664fd69334cedb9a7a064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F152112_1520d0fcbdd664fd69334cedb9a7a064.jpg&h=d30124ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aOP2WSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaOP2WSX.jpg&h=04383e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同埋麻煩以後要睇陳雲偉論請去高登會員香江19度睇，直程係陳雲代言人<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/user/403064/posthistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fuser%2F403064%2Fposthistory&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mIZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4553483b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/user/403064/posthistory</a>"},{"pid":"b54aff5b41e154e430644fc5008187b8f42ec481","tid":1570172,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:44:08.000Z","msg":"中秋係沙田成千人圍一個藍撕紙 望住比佢撕落黎 重要放佢走 一路走一路啱香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class